  "texts": [
    "The spectrumIn this section, we will discuss the spectrum of minimal tension strings on AdS 3 × S 3 × T 4 at the level of detail required for the current work.",
    "This section will draw heavily on the existing literature and will not contain novel results.",
    "20 There is, however, a slight difference in the interpretation of the b-ghost insertions in section 3.3 compared to the literature, where we view them as screening operators for U 0.",
    "Physical statesUsually, a theory of strings on AdS 3 (for generic k) would include both discrete and continuous representations [3,18].",
    "Classically, these correspond to bound states and scattering states, respectively."
  ]
